法規內容.條文內容:
Upon receiving the electronic trademark application documents that meet the requirements set forth in the preceding Article and are in absence of the circumstances prescribed under Paragraph 1 or 2 of Article 9, the Registrar Office shall notify the user of the receipt; such notification shall contain the following:
1. the mark of the Registrar Office;
2. the time of receipt of the complete electronic trademark application documents;
3. the accession number or application number of the electronic trademark application Documents referred to in the preceding subparagraph; and
4. a brief summary of the electronic trademark application documents received.
